Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是椿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見呢 居然在這種地方不期而遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 去買東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 去買衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是暑假末了 既然偶遇了就順便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪個店吃個冰淇林如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啥不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得同學之間遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6話 謎之升級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 椿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這家冷飲店的冰淇林很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是小學生的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有胸部在茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這個有點不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和丘兩人一起吃冰淇林的事被知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後會被上野訓的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 那個不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿被信任著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平和我一起的時候經常稱讚椿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然運動神經和成績都很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本性還是個好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是稱讚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上野的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘用名字叫上野的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是偶爾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 上野有時也會用名字叫丘你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為叫步子 所以會叫我步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卜部之間真無法想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然用名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非椿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在想象被喜歡的女孩用名字叫的情景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒在想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說剛開學的早晨 果然起不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就沒起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老姐沒叫醒我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 渾身乏力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期困乏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假啊 還想多要一個月左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 昨天有和丘說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 和丘？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 昨天沒說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什麼啊 很讓人在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 曬黑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了海邊之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 算是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你交到女朋友 然後和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和老姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和老姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 比起和男人一起要好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天在中央町和椿偶遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 難得遇上了 就兩人聊了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和上野偶爾不用姓而用名去相互稱呼的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了那個話題之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿就沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然用「明」叫了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他嚇到了 然後臉撞到冰淇林上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是在想象被卜部用名字叫的情景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿果然很讓人感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 熱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在想象被椿用名字叫你的情景了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那樣的話 為啥我臉會紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅了吧 我的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天太陽真毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍去公園休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買回來…了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要硬叫醒她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁買回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比在學校時睡得更沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我買果汁回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得不用叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是趁果汁還沒變溫時喝比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是笑臉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為被叫做「美琴」而高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴鳴蟬還在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明夏天都結束了 蟬真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 據說鳴鳴蟬在不同的地方叫聲會不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中國的鳴鳴蟬不是咪~咪咪咪的叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是咪咪咪咪~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用名字互稱還有點太早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 今天卜部的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部是我的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我拍一張卜部的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想至少要有一張自己女朋友的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你怎麼照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會數 3 2 1 拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩來一張滿臉笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要照的話就這個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了拍照而製造笑容是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想要張有笑容的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微笑一笑也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部今天好遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是椿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 畢竟初中三年都是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟椿也都在委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 椿 如果你不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在找一家咖啡廳坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多令人懷念的事情想說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在等人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天沒有空…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次有機會再說吧 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有沒有到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看椿聊得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不好打攪 就等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前椿給我看的照片裡的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿初中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單戀的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也拒絕了她邀請我去咖啡廳的提議…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我和早川去了咖啡廳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是打個比方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是假設
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能會有那種事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把嘴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果椿拋下我和她去了咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想會很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 現在從椿的眼裡所流下的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是椿比起我反而選擇了她的那時 我所流下的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早川的確是我以前的單戀對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天難得見面 覺得的確是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕邀請的時候 說實話我的確覺得可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在喜歡的是卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那絕對是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 保持這個表情不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把現在卜部的笑容拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你願意讓我拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會珍惜那張照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
